<TITLE>
Bootup, the American Indian Whale (Putup, Podab, Putep)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Bootup,
a whale who serves as the steed of the Wabanaki culture hero Glooskap.">
